Description: TLS/SSL certificate monitoring tool
 A GTK4/Adwaita application for monitoring TLS/SSL certificates.
 Tracks expiration dates, certificate chains, and alerts on
 upcoming expirations.
 .
 Features include automatic periodic checks, visual status
 indicators, and desktop notifications.
